This Lambda function serves as a backend to manage and query inventory information.

Available Function is getInventoryByProductCode
- Without product_code: Returns list of all products with their inventory levels and the prices
- With product_code: Returns inventory details for specific product and the prices

Input Format:
{
    "function": "string",
    "parameters": [
        {
            "name": "product_code",
            "value": "string"
        }
    ]
}

Sample Request:
{
    "function": "getInventoryByProductCode",
    "parameters": [
        {
            "name": "product_code",
            "value": "CM001"
        }
    ]
}

Sample Response:
{
    "name": "Meow Munchies",
    "quantity": 150,
    "last_updated": "ISO-8601 date",
    "status": "in_stock|low_stock|out_of_stock",
    "reorder_level": 50,
    "price": 24.99
}
